<p><b>Peter Stephen Paul Brook</b> <a href="Companion_of_Honour" title="Companion of Honour" class="mw-redirect">CH</a>, <a href="Order_of_the_British_Empire" title="Order of the British Empire">CBE</a> (born 21 March 1925) is an English <a href="Theatre_director" title="Theatre director">theatre</a> and <a href="Film_director" title="Film director">film director</a> and innovator, who has been based in France since the early 1970s.</p>
